Package: OpTop
Type: Package
Title: Optimal Topic Selection and Goodness-of-Fit for LDA Models
Version: 0.9.9
Authors@R: c( 
    person("Francesco", "Grossetti", email = "francesco.grossetti@unibocconi.it", 
    role = c("cre", "aut", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5130-7745")), 
    person("Craig", "Lewis", email = "craig.lewis@owen.vanderbilt.edu", role = c("aut", "cph")),
    person("Mattia", "Tamellini", email = "mattia.tamellini@gmail.com", role = "ctb"))
Description: Implements statistical tests and discrepancy indices to select the optimal number of
    topics and compare goodness-of-fit across Latent Dirichlet Allocation models, following
    the optimal topic identification approach of Lewis and Grossetti (2022)
    <https://jmlr.org/papers/v23/19-297.html>.
